Game Title: Enchanted Forest: Defense of the Magic Tree

In Enchanted Forest: Defense of the Magic Tree" the player 
plays a wizard that has been tasked with defending the Magic Tree 
found at the center of the map from an oncoming horde of Ghosts.
The wizard has limited magic bolts, but they can be replenished 
by picking up coins found around the map. The player loses when 
the Ghosts either destroy the tree or kill the wizard.

Requirements:
arcade
random
math
 

